Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 26 October 2016 (13 days before demonetization). Dark artistic image with text: 'AND THEN, GOD CREATED THE.. 8 SCORPIO' with a woman lying in flames/fire imagery. Credited 'Noorie Rai.' DECODED: Framing the number 8 and Scorpio as divinely ordained. Fire imagery = destruction/purification (demonetization as purification of black money). 'God created' = divine hand behind the event. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Divine Justice — the coming demonetization as a divinely sanctioned karmic event.